\c 30
\s Abantwana bakoIsrayeli bazabusiswa ngokuphenduka langokulalela
\p
\v 1 Kuzakuthi-ke\x + Levi 26.40-42.\x*, zonke izinto lezi sezikwehlele, isibusiso lesiqalekiso, engizibekileyo phambi kwakho\x + 11.26. Dute. 28.\x*, uzivuselele enhliziyweni yakho phakathi kwezizwe zonke lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekuxotshele khona\x + 4.29-31. 1 Kho. 8.47-50.\x*,
\v 2 uzabuyela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho, ulalele ilizwi layo, njengakho konke engikulaya khona lamuhla, wena labantwana bakho, ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke\x + Isa. 55.7. Lilo 3.40. Jow. 2.12,13.\x*,
\v 3 khona iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izabuyisa ukuthunjwa kwakho, ikuhawukele\x + Hlab. 126.1,4. Jer. 29.14.\x*, ibuye, ikubuthe ezizweni zonke lapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ekuhlakazele khona\x + Jer. 32.37. Hez. 34.13. 36.24.\x*.
\v 4 Lanxa abaxotshiweyo bakho besemkhawulweni wamazulu, ulapho iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubutha, ulapho-ke ikuthathe\x + Neh. 1.9. Dute. 28.64.\x*.
\v 5 LeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakungenisa elizweni oyihlo abalifuyayo, njalo uzalifuya, ikwenzele okuhle, ikwandise kulaboyihlo\x + 28.63.\x*.
\v 6 LeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izasoka inhliziyo yakho lenhliziyo yenzalo yakho, ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke, ukuze uphile\x + 10.16.\x*.
\v 7 LeN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakwehlisela zonke leziziqalekiso ezitheni zakho lakwabakuzondayo ababekuzingela.
\v 8 Wena-ke uzabuya ulalele ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd*, wenze yonke imilayo yayo engikulaya yona lamuhla.
\v 9 Njalo iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakwandisa kuwo wonke umsebenzi wesandla sakho, esithelweni sesizalo sakho, lesithelweni sezifuyo zakho, lesithelweni somhlaba wakho, ukuthi kulunge\x + 28.11.\x*; ngoba iN\nd kosi\nd* izabuya ukukuthabela kube kuhle, njengalokhu yathabela oyihlo\x + 28.63.\x*,
\v 10 uba uzalalela ilizwi leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukugcina imilayo yayo lezimiso zayo ezibhalwe kulolugwalo lomlayo, uba uphendukela eN\nd kosi\nd*ni uNkulunkulu wakho ngenhliziyo yakho yonke langomphefumulo wakho wonke.
\p
\v 11 Ngoba lumlayo engikulaya wona lamuhla kawufihlwanga kuwe, futhi kawukhatshana lawe.
\v 12 Kawukho emazulwini ukuthi uthi: Ngubani ozasenyukelela emazulwini, asithathele wona ukuze siwuzwe siwenze\x + Roma 10.6-8.\x*?
\v 13 Futhi kawungaphetsheya kolwandle ukuthi uthi: Ngubani ozasichaphela aye ngaphetsheya kolwandle, asithathele wona ukuze siwuzwe siwenze?
\v 14 Kodwa ilizwi liseduze kakhulu lawe, emlonyeni wakho lenhliziyweni yakho ukulenza.
\p
\v 15 Bona, ngibekile phambi kwakho lamuhla impilo lokulunga, lokufa lobubi\x + 30.19.\x*.
\v 16 Ngoba ngiyakulaya lamuhla ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, lokuhamba endleleni zayo, lokugcina imilayo yayo lezimiso zayo lezahlulelo zayo, ukuze uphile wande\x + 30.6; 6.5.\x*; leN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho izakubusisa elizweni oya kulo ukudla ilifa lalo.
\v 17 Kodwa uba inhliziyo yakho iphenduka ukuze ungalaleli\x + 29.18.\x*, uduhiswe, ukhothamele abanye onkulunkulu, ubakhonze\x + 4.19.\x*,
\v 18 ngiyalitshela lamuhla ukuthi lizabhubha lokubhubha\x + 26.3.\x*; kaliyikwelula izinsuku elizweni lapho ochaphela iJordani khona ukungena kulo ukudla ilifa lalo\x + 4.26. 31.28.\x*.
\v 19 Lamuhla ngiyabiza amazulu lomhlaba ukufakaza ngani\x + 4.26. 31.28.\x*. Impilo lokufa ngikubekile phambi kwakho\x + 30.15. 32.47.\x*, isibusiso lesiqalekiso. Ngakho khetha impilo ukuze uphile wena lenzalo yakho\x + 30.1.\x*,
\v 20 ukuthanda iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho, ukulalela ilizwi layo, lokunamathela kuyo\x + 10.20.\x*. Ngoba iyimpilo yakho lobude bensuku zakho\x + Hlab. 27.1. 66.9. Joha. 11.25.\x*, ukuze uhlale elizweni iN\nd kosi\nd* uNkulunkulu wakho eyafungela oyihlo, uAbrahama, uIsaka, loJakobe, ukubanika lona\x + Gen. 50.24.\x*.